@startuml
actor App 
box "Runtime"
participant Orchestrator
database GlobalNode
database LocalNodes
end box

App -[#green]> Orchestrator: Request:\nAlgorithm, data, filters, transformation
Orchestrator -[#blue]-> LocalNodes: Control:\nTransformation
LocalNodes -[#red]> LocalNodes: Transform:\nCreate new table,\n\tview, ...
ref over Orchestrator, LocalNodes, GlobalNode : Algorithm
Orchestrator -[#green]> App: Response:\nFinal result
@enduml

